_aChangeLog.text: Added a couple of blocks for slightly better route viability
Changed the textures on the sides of the blocks
Improved/basically fixed seeing large areas of the map through the sky
Added lights in dark areas and some plants
Added a direction indicator texture on the block below the drop

_sText:
This map was made on stream in 2 hours for a little speed mapping challenge.
A lot of known issues, but it'll remain as-is for a couple days so that I don't get harassed by my viewers for actually putting more than the allotted time into it. >.>

It was made with 100t 1000aa autobhop in mind, absolutely not tested on scroll, although it's probably possible.
